var_dump(empty($config['installedpackages']));
bool(false)
var_dump(empty($config['crud']));
bool(true)

empty() on something that is not set returns true, just the same as if it is set to the blank string, or an empty array, or the number 0.
So just empty()=true does not mean it is set.

